e1d7048b9d0ddefccd62408a8fa12e7.webp 200w,\n/static/33bc97ff6db7be2793b8f12037eb8d89/1f5c5/7e1d7048b9d0ddefccd62408a8fa12e7.webp 400w,\n/static/33bc97ff6db7be2793b8f12037eb8d89/58556/7e1d7048b9d0ddefccd62408a8fa12e7.webp 800w,\n/static/33bc97ff6db7be2793b8f12037eb8d89/24134/7e1d7048b9d0ddefccd62408a8fa12e7.webp 1181w","sizes":"(max-width: 800px) 100vw, 800px"}}},"title":"MXC to Donate €200,000 to Berlin Vietnamese Market","post":{"content":"## MXC to Donate €200,000 to Berlin Vietnamese Market\nMXC working to add early fire detection systems in Berlin, Jeff is back from China and we are releasing the largest news in MXC history, later this week. Welcome to this week’s news update.\n\nMXC is working with hardware partner MatchX to donate 200.000 Euros worth of fire detection systems to the Dong Xi’an center in Berlin. This past week the Vietnamese market experienced a tragic fire that early detection could have reduced. To this end, we will supply the center with fire detection sensors, an AI-enabled LPWAN camera, and an LPWAN gateway.\n\nJeff is back from his trip to China and his epic move across Berlin. While in China he met with the Shanghai Yangpu District Government to check on the progress of the Shanghai project. He also met with MXC supporter Fenbushi, as well as a number of interested companies on the Nanjing Tech Week Exhibit floor.\n\nKeep your eyes on MXC this week as some epic news is about to be released. Can’t say more in this now, but be sure to follow all of the MXC channels to keep up-to-date on the latest news.\n\nThis has been this week’s news update. I look forward to speaking with all of you again next week. Until then, get active, get in the community, as us questions — because it’s only together that we can build the Future of IoT.","date":"July 08, 2019","metaDescription":"Following a recent firey disaster at Dong Xuan Center in Berlin, MXC and MatchX are donating €200,000 worth of fire prevention equipment.","video":null,"slug":"mxc-to-donate-e200000-to-berlin-vietnamese-market"},"tags":[{"tag":"Community Engagement","slug":"community-engagement"},{"tag":"Dong Xuang Center Fire","slug":"dong-xuang-center-fire"},{"tag":"MXC Donation","slug":"mxc-donation"},{"tag":"Fire Prevention","slug":"fire-prevention"},{"tag":"MXC","slug":"mxc"}],"author":{"author":"Siwon Kim","slug":"siwon-kim"},"zhch_post":{"post":{"slug":"mxc极域捐赠20万欧元到柏林的越南市场"}},"zhtw_post":{"post":{"slug":"mxc極域捐贈20萬歐元到柏林的越南市場"}},"ko_post":null},"hans":{"category":{"zhchCategory":"新闻更新","zhchSlug":"新闻更新"},"featuredImage":null,"title":"MXC极域捐赠20万欧元到柏林的越南市场","post":{"content":"## MXC极域捐赠20万欧元到柏林的越南市场\n\nMXC极域致力于开发柏林早期火灾探测系统，Jeff从中国回来啦！我们将在本周晚些时候发布MXC极域史上最大的新闻。 欢迎回到本周的新闻更新。\n\nMXC极域正与硬体合作伙伴MatchX合作，向柏林东宣中心捐赠价值20万欧元的火灾探测系统。 过去一周，这个柏林最大的越南市场经历了一场悲剧性的火灾，尽早地发现可以极大地减少损失。 为此，我们将为他们提供火灾探测感应器，支持AI的LPWAN摄影机和LPWAN闸道器。\n\nJeff结束了他在中国的精彩旅程，回到柏林啦！ 在中国期间，他与上海杨浦区政府会面，了解上海项目的进展情况。 他还会见了MXC极域的支持者，分布式资本，以及南京科技周展览中一些感兴趣的公司。\n\n本周请继续关注MXC极域哦。因为一些重大新闻即将发布！ 现在还不能说哟~ 但请务必关注所有的MXC极域频道，以便您及时了解最新的消息。\n\n这就是本周的新闻更新啦。 我很期待下周再跟你们聊聊。 在那之前，变得积极吧、加入我们的社群、问我们问题。因为只有我们在一起，我们才能建造物联网的未来。","date":"July 08, 2019","metaDescription":"MXC极域致力于开发柏林早期火灾探测系统，Jeff从中国回来啦！我们将在本周晚些时候发布MXC极域史上最大的新闻。 欢迎回到本周的新闻更新！","video":"https://www.youtube.com/embed/EB8cYorQ1gU","slug":"mxc极域捐赠20万欧元到柏林的越南市场"},"tags":[{"zhchTag":"MXC极域捐赠","zhchSlug":"MXC极域捐赠"}],"author":{"author":"Siwon Kim","slug":"siwon-kim"},"enPost":{"post":{"slug":"mxc-to-donate-e200000-to-berlin-vietnamese-market"}}},"hant":{"category":{"zhchCategory":"新闻更新","zhchSlug":"新闻更新"},"featuredImage":null,"title":"MXC极域捐赠20万欧元到柏林的越南市场","post":{"content":"## MXC极域捐赠20万欧元到柏林的越南市场\n\nMXC极域致力于开发柏林早期火灾探测系统，Jeff从中国回来啦！我们将在本周晚些时候发布MXC极域史上最大的新闻。 欢迎回到本周的新闻更新。\n\nMXC极域正与硬体合作伙伴MatchX合作，向柏林东宣中心捐赠价值20万欧元的火灾探测系统。 过去一周，这个柏林最大的越南市场经历了一场悲剧性的火灾，尽早地发现可以极大地减少损失。 为此，我们将为他们提供火灾探测感应器，支持AI的LPWAN摄影机和LPWAN闸道器。\n\nJeff结束了他在中国的精彩旅程，回到柏林啦！ 在中国期间，他与上海杨浦区政府会面，了解上海项目的进展情况。 他还会见了MXC极域的支持者，分布式资本，以及南京科技周展览中一些感兴趣的公司。\n\n本周请继续关注MXC极域哦。因为一些重大新闻即将发布！ 现在还不能说哟~ 但请务必关注所有的MXC极域频道，以便您及时了解最